                    "value": 1400,
                    "currency": "gp"
                },
                "text": "You recover 1d4 Hit Points instead of 1 Hit Point when casting divine spells from your spell slots. Change the beads\u2019 list of spells to the 4th-level versions of bless , divine wrath (matching one component of your deity\u2019s alignment), heal , neutralize poison , and remove disease . You can cast each of these once per day.",
